a id=\"top\"></a>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n\t\t\t<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Ring of Thunder</h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From CrawlWiki</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\" class=\"mw-jump\">\n\t\t\t\t\tJump to:\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#mw-head\">navigation</a>, \t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#p-search\">search</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div style=\"border: 1px solid #f00; background-color: #fcc; border-left: 15px solid #f00; margin-bottom: 20px; width: 100%; padding: 4px 10px; line-height: 1.1em; width: auto;\"><i><b>Obsolete</b>: This article refers to an aspect of the game which has been removed. It is retained for historical reference only.</i></div>\n<table style=\"background:#f5faff; border:1px solid #cedff2; width:auto; margin: 0px 5%; margin-bottom:1.25em; font-style:italic; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:1.5em 1em;\">\n\n<tr>\n<td>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 100%;\"> Surrounds the caster with a mobile ring of highly-damaging thunderclouds.\n</td></tr></table>\n<p><b>Ring of Thunder</b> is a monster-only spell that surrounds the user with a ring of <a href=\"/Cloud#Thunder\" title=\"Cloud\">thunder clouds</a>, which periodically deal heavy <a href=\"/Electricity\" title=\"Electricity\">electricity</a> damage to creatures standing in them. Much like <a href=\"/Ring_of_Flames\" title=\"Ring of Flames\">Ring of Flames</a>, new clouds are constantly created around the user as they move.\n</p><p>The following enemies cast Ring of Thunder:\n</p>\n<ul><li> <span class=\"nhsym clr-brightcyan\">D</span> <a href=\"/File:Bai_Suzhen_(dragon).png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bai Suzhen (dragon).png\" src=\"/images/7/7c/Bai_Suzhen_%28dragon%29.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/Bai_Suzhen_(dragon)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bai Suzhen (dragon)\">Bai Suzhen (dragon)</a></b></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span></h2>\n<ul><li>This spell was removed in <a href=\"/0.26\" title=\"0.26\">0.26</a>. Instead, <a href=\"/Bai_Suzhen#Dragon_Form\" title=\"Bai Suzhen\">Bai Suzhen</a> and some <a href=\"/Pandemonium_lord\" title=\"Pandemonium lord\">pandemonium lords</a> got a permanent <b>Ring of X</b> enchantment that surrounds them with an appropriate cloud ring.</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240916224944\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\n[SMW] In‐text annotation parser time: 0.001 seconds\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.168 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 31/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 146/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 821/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 150/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 5/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nLua time usage: 0.050s\nLua virtual size: 12.15 MB / 50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  117.139      1 -total\n 95.96%  112.409      1 Template:Monsterlink\n 93.88%  109.967      1 Template:Glyph\n  1.94%    2.271      1 Template:Obsolete\n  1.68%    1.968      1 Template:Flavour\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key crawl_wiki-crawl_:pcache:idhash:9838-0!canonical and timestamp 20240916224944 and revision id 56708\n -->\n</div>\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"printfooter\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\tRetrieved from \"<a dir=\"ltr\" href=\"http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Ring_of_Thunder&amp;oldid=56708\">http://crawl.chaosforge.org/index.php?title=Ring_of_Thunder&amp;oldid=56708</a>\"\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"catlinks\" class=\"catlinks\" data-mw=\"interface\"><div id=\"mw-normal-catlinks\" class=\"mw-normal-catlinks\"